Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.87,0:00:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura... Chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Homemade... is probably a bit heavy.\NI've never cooked before, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just buy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.89,0:00:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,On February 14th, I was going\Nto go somewhere with Shimamura
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and exchange chocolates with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.44,0:00:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:40.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,It'll be exciting to see what Hyodo\Ncan do with their record next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I need to ask her what she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:46.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,And now, the moment everyone's\Nbeen waiting for, romance horoscopes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to make sure I don't regret anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Shaman Taoka's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...Romance horoscopes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:58.80,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Shaman Taoka's Romance Horoscopes"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to tell you all about\Nyour romance luck again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.53,0:01:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.12,0:01:26.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Missed Call Just Now Tarumi"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tarumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.04,0:01:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a call when I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:18.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Libra"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I see some rough times ahead\Nfor the Libras today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you're aware of your surroundings!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's lucky letter is... D!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want something? Like milk tea or bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:04:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Say... what's your sign, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure. I was born in April...\NOh, April 10th.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means she's an Aries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If she's an Aries, I think our\Ncompatibility sucks, since I'm a Libra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.88,0:04:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'd want to get closer\Nto someone who's not compatible...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you want to know my sign,\Nanyway? Are you into astrology?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I, uh... I need to get\Nready for our next class...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least I managed to find out\Nwhen Shimamura's birthday is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Tarumi"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, um... What kind of chocolate do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... I think I'm a fan of\Nmilk chocolate. It goes down better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:34.04,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Libra"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bam, tap, bam, tap, bam, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Libras...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Change up your hairstyle\Nto really grab your crush's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's lucky letter is A.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wanna have lunch together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, is that all chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you, like, use your head too much\Nstudying that you need the extra carbs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, your ponytail's cute.\NThough I like you just the way you are usually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,U-U... Usually?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Your chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Milk chocolate, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Though I like you\Njust the way you are usually."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Say how you really feel today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know when you're gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Die! Die! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I became a lot more positive\Nafter meeting Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm so positive\Nthat I'm about to burst,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but my days are now brighter, nonetheless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to tell her\Nhow much I appreciate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura is my sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just, um...\Nwanted to talk about the sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not that part! You wanted to show gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Gratitude, gratitude,\Nhow do I show gratitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything to\Nget thanked... Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I became\Nmore positive or just stupider.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Libras out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,make sure you hurry up and\Ngive them your homemade chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it! Your lucky letter today is C!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:36.64,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Chocolate They'll Think Is Delicious"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this... Chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:55.49,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Well?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"Well?" "Well?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:08:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I'd feel awkward\Nif someone sent this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want Shimamura to be happy.\NI want her to think I'm special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My wishes and desires kept piling up\Nfar and high like mountain ranges,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but what I was seeing before me\Nwas an endless wasteland.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It was better off before I messed with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.82,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Tarumi Incoming Call"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tarumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shima?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I didn't call you back earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine. We haven't\Ntalked since grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to mention this the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really happy to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:10:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Also... That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it? Happy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... I guess I don't mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, look at that hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what shocks you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura, let's go see a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you two go? I've gotta study.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Go with them. And make sure they get some lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:52.36,On Top,,0,0,0,,Let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I spotted some teacher\Nwith some kids, but it's Shimamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hino... Why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just got back from some family business.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Hino. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um... Who might you be? Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess you've been dragging the runts\Naround today on a family discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to see a movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Nagafuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't hang out on our days off, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Though maybe I'll go buy some\Nchocolate on my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you giving some to Nagafuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's more like I'll give it to her\Nand we'll both eat it on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We do that every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... So, why do you buy Nagafuji chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because it makes Nagafuji happy?\NAnd we both like chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:52.85,On Top,,0,0,0,,Spinny, spin... Spinny, spin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:12:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's all there is\Nto a girls' Valentine's together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi's way too eager... And she's too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we're both overthinking\NValentine's Day way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You and your destined prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...have an exciting encounter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna play some games.\NWanna go to Nagafuji's house with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know much about games, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, I'm not going to twist your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! The gang's all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:59.48,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Chief Adachi: 5,000,000 yen"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Another six. Looks like you're off\Nto a great start, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it's my turn... now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:10.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Nagafuji Pro: 6,500,000 yen"\N"Nippon Budokan"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You just need to keep squishing your boobs. Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:17.79,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Mrs. Hino: 15,000,000 yen"\N"Sunshine 60"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, nice! Hup...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A one? Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. Have some fresh croquettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck yeah! Love you, Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is lively today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Hino went off to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuffup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do in Hokkaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:45.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Mrs. Hino: 27,000,000 yen"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I got Okinawa.\NThe goal is Nagoya, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Dang it, I got a one again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Adachicchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only four spaces from the goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a four. You've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Chief Adachi: 52,000,000 yen"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:09.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Nagoya Castle"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a four.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, the first one in's Adacchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. That means I'm in last place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:31.74,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Nagafuji Butcher Shop"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You were in last place until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Only people with bad personalities\Nare good at this game,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,so I guess you're a great person, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I do think you're a great person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We can play again some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful getting home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you at least have some fun, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Actually, I think\NI asked you this before, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, want me to give you a ride home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be really out of the way. Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem way different from when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Time passes by so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just being trifled with in this\Ncompletely different flow of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, in three days...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't forgotten about the chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Adachi! Eyes up front!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure Shimamura is stealing my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But that time, unlike the\Ncolorless days I've spent,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is so filled with light, just like a jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two! One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap... I might not make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two! One, two! One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it isn't Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly. Or rather, aren't you cold?\NLook at what you're wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you're cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a fine adult, so I don't have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,An adult, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not showing up to school at that age,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you're heading right down the path\Nto becoming a delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:17:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you know, Shimamura,\NI'm around 680 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I actually have school,\Nso see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This ninja art is quite useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninja art?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninja Art: Make Them Turn Around\NBy Staring at Them. {\i1}Nin, nin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninja art, my ass. I just came back\Nbecause I'm a really good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, yesh. You sure are\Na good pershon, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. So thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:01.08,On Top,,0,0,0,,"I see, thanks"\N"You're not coming today?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.08,0:18:02.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,"I see, thanks"\N"Unread: You're not coming today?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:06.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Unread: You're not coming today?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to get closer,\Nyou need to make the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't keep waiting forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.26,0:18:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I believe your name was Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... So, where's Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She's taking a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So make sure you shh! Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I must go procure dinner soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I leave this to you, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Hey, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So where's Yashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... She said something about procuring dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure does whatever she wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So what brings you here, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well, you weren't at school today,\Nso I thought you maybe had a cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent you a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A message?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I left it in my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why I came to see how you were doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but I guess I might've woken you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty decent, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.77,0:19:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When she looks like this,\NI can tell what Adachi wants from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Something she can lean onto that'll support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Previously, it was the gym wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But at some point, that turned into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I don't wonder about why that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but the fact of the matter is, I am indeed\Nspending time with Adachi like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's lucky letter is A!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This lucky letter was passed down\Nfrom my great ancestor, Himi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait... D-Don't forget to buy chocolates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I need to buy chocolate today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:21:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Adachi wants to go back to that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we insisted on going\Nto that place right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd probably freeze\Nand wouldn't be able to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The seasons continue to change,\Nand we go along for the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dandan {\i0}noodles and a\Nhalf order of fried rice up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to call you in suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do though?\NI was planning on buying chocolate today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:37.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Tarumi Incoming Call"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shima? Sorry to call you out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, are you free right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Chocolate... Chocolate...\NChocolate for Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.35,0:22:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going out with Shimamura tomorrow,\Nso I guess I can just pick then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.62,0:22:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tarumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.21,0:22:22.05,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 8 'The Briar That\NWeaves the Past: Old Rose'"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Heyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Heya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.01,0:24:07.00,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Next Time: 'Love That Embraces\Nthe Holy Mother: Marigold'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.78,0:23:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: Fortunetelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.08,0:23:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I see it! I see your future!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:24:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you figured out\Nthat I'm going to kiss you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where does it say that I'm going to kiss you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.29,0:24:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... The forehead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know about that...
